 * $ scribblec.sh modules/core/src/test/scrib/demo/betty16/lec2/smtp/Smtp.scr -d modules/core/src/test/scrib/ -api Smtp C
 * 
 * (2) Generate Endpoint API for C with session subtyping interfaces
